**Why this saves writing:**\
\
The mechanism truth is authored ONCE per topic. Social anxiety uses the same engines (avoidance, safety_behavior, anticipation) regardless of persona. The arc structures are the same. The role contracts are the same. What changes is templates (voice) and variables (world). That's exactly what Phoenix is built to do.\
\
