\
### What You Author Per Tier\
\
**Tier 1 topic (e.g., Social Anxiety):**\
- 3\'964 engines with full mechanism definitions \uc0\u8594  authored once\
- Master arc(s) per engine \uc0\u8594  authored once\
- STORY atoms per (persona \'d7 engine \'d7 role) \uc0\u8594  this is the main writing\
- REFLECTION, EXERCISE, INTEGRATION atoms per (persona \'d7 topic) \uc0\u8594  authored per persona\
- Compression atoms per (persona \'d7 topic) \uc0\u8594  authored per persona\
\
**Tier 2:** Same structure, but mid-length format means fewer chapters, fewer atoms needed per book.\
\
**Tier 3:** Short format. Can often reuse engines from Tier 1 topics (driving anxiety reuses avoidance engine from social anxiety). Minimal new atom authoring.\
\
