\
## 4. The "Anxiety Wrapper" Idea \'97 Series-Level Metadata Inheritance\
\
You asked: *Do I have to write all metadata stuff for each sub book in a series?*\
\
**No. Build series wrappers.**\
\
A series wrapper is a YAML config that provides defaults for every book in the series. Individual books inherit and override only what's different.\
\
### Proposed: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "app://-/index.html#"}}{\fldrslt \cf14 anxiety_series.yaml}}\

\f2 yaml\
series_id: anxiety_mastery\
series_title: "The Anxiety Mastery Series"\
domain: anxiety\
brand_id: phoenix_core          # inherited by all books\
default_author_id: luna_hart    # override per book if needed\
default_narrator_id: narrator_01\
default_positioning_profile: somatic_companion\
\
# Series-level metadata (inherited by all books)\
series_metadata:\
  category: "Health & Wellness > Mental Health > Anxiety"\
  keywords_shared:\
    - anxiety\
    - anxiety relief\
    - therapeutic audiobook\
    - nervous system regulation\
  target_age: "18-45"\
\
# Per-installment overrides\
installments:\
  - installment: 1\
    topic_id: social_anxiety\
    tier: 1\
    duration_class: full\
    title_template: "Social Anxiety: \{\{persona_hook\}\}"\
    keywords_specific:\
      - social anxiety\
      - social phobia\
      - social anxiety audiobook\
    engines: [avoidance, safety_behavior, anticipation]\
    # arc, author, narrator inherited from series defaults\
\
  - installment: 2\
    topic_id: panic_attacks\
    tier: 1\
    duration_class: full\
    title_template: "Panic Attacks: \{\{persona_hook\}\}"\
    keywords_specific:\
      - panic attacks\
      - panic disorder\
      - panic attack help\
    engines: [false_alarm, loop, catastrophizing]\
\
  - installment: 3\
    topic_id: overthinking\
    tier: 1\
    duration_class: full\
    title_template: "Overthinking: \{\{persona_hook\}\}"\
    keywords_specific:\
      - overthinking\
      - rumination\
      - anxious thoughts\
    engines: [loop, cognitive_fusion, control_paradox]
\f0 \
### What the wrapper saves you:\
\
| Without wrapper | With wrapper |\
|---|---|\
| Set brand_id for each book | Set once in series |\
| Set author for each book | Set once, override when needed |\
| Set narrator for each book | Set once |\
| Set category/keywords from scratch | Inherit shared, add specific |\
| Set positioning_profile per book | Set once |\
| Manually track installment order | Declared in config |\
| No cross-book diversity enforcement | Planner reads full series config |\
\
